      <item>
        <title>Introducing Shiori: A Bootstrap-Based Jekyll Theme</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/992008/3955483/2b9a77ae-2702-11e4-9f28-6afb051271de.png&quot; alt=&quot;Shiori&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

